title: Sen. Patty Murray slams Trump’s abortion ban for veterans - Thu, 25 Dec 2025 PST
description: Sen. Patty Murray criticized a Trump administration overhaul to veterans’ abortion access this week after the Justice Department issued an opinion barring the federal government from providing abortion services to veterans and their dependents in cases of rape, incest or when the pregnancy threatens their health.
